(10968236, 1, 839, 'http://openagenda.com/event/public-funding_168', 'Cap Omega, le vendredi 28 avril 2017 à  09:00', 'BIC Montpellier - Masterclass - Public Funding', 'The best way to rise public funding for your innovative projects and start-ups in France', 'Good key and good process to take profit from early stage public funding:\n\n-Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  Tax Credit for Innovation; Tax credit for research; Young Innovative Company status\n\n-Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  Financial supports for innovation; Loans for the preparation phase of fundraising;\n\n-Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  Funding schemes for early stage startup; Collaborative project funding; Local/regional supports\n\nSpeaker:\n\nEfficient Innovation is a consulting company specialized in innovation management & funding. Founded in 1998, company''s headqarter is based in Montpellier and implanted teams and offices in Sao Paulo, Paris, Lyon, Aix-en-Provence, Toulouse, Bordeaux and Nantes (and one representative in Nancy).\n\nWith 80 engineers, doctors and academics, they are specialized in Innovation consulting, funding project management and training for start-up companies, mids caps and institutions.', '', '43.618677,3.912646', 'On registration', '', '2017-07-18 23:44:03', '2017-04-28', '18:59:39', '2017-04-28', '06:47:45'),
