érents programmes, le CFSI coordonne la campagne et le Festival ALIMENTERRE.\n\n\nLieau: Salle Jean Dame, 17 rue Leopold Bellan 75002 Paris', '', '43.634305,3.865814', '', '26,557,740,362,342,598,034,256,633,528,320', '2015-11-18 16:19:46', '2015-10-15', '07:41:15', '2015-10-15', '20:31:58'),
